      "en": {
        "name": "Kalashnikov AK-107 5.45x39 Assault Rifle",
        "shortName": "AK-107",
        "description": "The AK-107 is a Russian 5.45x39mm assault rifle developed from the AK-100-series. It features a 'balanced' operating system, similar to that used in the AEK-971. In this case, the designation AK does not indicate Avtomat Kalashnikova but Alexandrov/Kalashnikov. The revised designation indicates the incorporation of a new gas system, designed by Youriy Alexandrov, for Kalashnikov-pattern rifles."
